<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>103</hymn_number>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Tuanbia hlun kha ka theih cang, Khamhtu ratnak le sunparnak, Kalvary
 ah a nunnak a hloh, Mi tha lo khamh awkah, A hramnak aw ka theih cang,
 Thi thiang tlanhnak aw thlum a si. Cun ka sualnak kaa ngaichih i, Teinak
 kha ka hmuh cang.

[C1]
   Aw! Jesuh thawng in teinak, Ka thlarau ca zungzal A ka kawl i
   tlanhnak thi he a ka ratpi; Ka hngalh hlan in a ka dawt, Ka dawt ve awk a
   si ko, Tei dingin a ka kalpi, Thiannak thisen chungah.

[V2]
 Damter tu a si ka hngalh, Thianter khotu a sinak zong, Kebei mi lam an
 kal kho than i, Mitcaw nih khua an hmuh, &quot;Jesuh ra law ka damter, Ka
 lungthin vialte,&quot; tiah ka au, Jesuh ka sin ah a ra i, Teinak kha a ka pek.

[C2]
   Aw! Jesuh thawng in teinak, Ka thlarau ca zungzal A ka kawl i
   tlanhnak thi he a ka ratpi; Ka hngalh hlan in a ka dawt, Ka dawt ve awk a
   si ko, Tei dingin a ka kalpi, Thiannak thisen chungah.

[V3]
 Umnak a remh cang ka hngalh, Keimah ca ah a sungmi inn, Sui an phahmi
 lam kong zong ka theih, Lungvar umnak pinah, Vanmi hna hlasaknak le, A
 kan tlanhnak tuanbia hlun cu, Cu ni ah cun ka sa ve lai, Teinak hla
 sunglawi cu.

[C3]
   Aw! Jesuh thawng in teinak, Ka thlarau ca zungzal A ka kawl i
   tlanhnak thi he a ka ratpi; Ka hngalh hlan in a ka dawt, Ka dawt ve awk a
   si ko, Tei dingin a ka kalpi, Thiannak thisen chungah.</lyrics>
<title>JESUH THAWNG IN TEINAK CH103</title>
</song>